when he got off the airplane and got in the car, when 
he hit the news end, he went in the booth so they

46:25.418 --> 46:44.045
could, you know, fix him all up, cosmetic wires, 
hit television. I thought Reagan was the only one

46:44.065 --> 46:47.269
that did that. Excellent. Did that quite a bit. 
This was excellent. I'm kidding. That is

46:52.457 --> 46:54.700
fantastic. So every time Mr. Nixon went to a new 
area, he'd have a little... Every time Mr. Nixon

